Our products accompany you all year round and make outdoor work easier. Green wire - strong helper Garden applications Plant support: Support when attaching heavy plants to trellises or plant stakes. Building trellis aids: Climbing plants such as Vines, ivy or clematis can be easily attached to trellises thanks to binding wire and thus strengthen growth. Attach garden decorations: To protect garden lanterns or fairy lights from wind, a discreet attachment with a binding wire is often sufficient.
